Subject to the approval of the commission, the executive director shall:
Employ clerical and other staff assistance;
Prepare an annual report on the status of services to the deaf and hard of hearing;
Promote the training of interpreters for the deaf and hard of hearing;
Identify public and private agencies that provide services to the deaf and hard of hearing and cooperate in the coordination and development of these services;
Survey the needs and compile a census of the deaf and hard of hearing.
